transcript: Whoever you are, thank you! Without your help, we wouldn't be alive and well... How's my steak, bro? Raw, needs more cooking SNACK BREAK? GIVE ME SOME  How's the human? Raw, needs more cooking... Situation is the worst... After capturing our titan... Enemy has accessed our transmissions... Many of our secret locations were compromised... We immediately cut intel off... But it's only a matter of time... Until they find us all. We're blind now... There were unionized group of researchers in Eastern Europe... Their status is unknown... You need to rescue and deliver the survivors... If there's still any... Most importantly... Do not die. And you. Staying on base? It's now or never... We shall join the battlefield. GET OVER HERE! DEPARTING NOW! Hugs? ;) NO CHANCE GRAB ONTO SOMETHING ELSE YOU THINK THIS IS FUNNY? THAT WE ARE... SOME KIND OF 'FELLAS' NOW? Yes! YOU ARE WRONG DO YOU POSSESS EVEN DIMLIEST CONCEPT OF WHAT THIS PLACE IS? IS IT FUTURE? OR IS IT PAST? WHAT RESIDES IN THE CORNERS OF THIS DARKNESS ANDWHAT HAPPENS WHEN OUTSIDE ENTITY STAYS THERE FOR TOO LONG... ONE OF US HAS THE ANSWER... JEFFREY WOULDN'T MIND SOME COMPANY LOCK IN APPROACHING DESTINATION PERFECT TIMING Lord, forgive me... I'm gonna fluffin kill! I SURRENDE- No prisoners, bozo! Rest in shit! This will be painful... YOU'RE SCREWED! *unscrews* Nice job, friend! WATCH YO BACK, DUMBASS! What the sigma? DEPARTING! If that's where my life should end... So be it... What? It's over... Fate of your men is already sealed! Say your final words! Can't believe the last thing I'll see is...  Your ugly madufaqin face. Wot? This merely delays your defeat... We need to retreat! NO MORE HIDING! ALL INVADERS WILL BE EXECUTED
